quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  67,15,"Niyo yagize Isi ngo ishobore gukora kubera mwebwe, rero ni mugenzure kumpande zayo zose, kandi mufungure kumigisha yayo, no kuriyo niho twese tuzo subirayo"
  67,16,"Mbega mwiyumvira yuko muri mumahoro ku Mana iyo mw’ijuru itazoba cinyiriza kw’Isi, mukaza mubona Isi iranyiganze"
  67,17,"Canke mwiyumvira yuko muri mumahoro ku Mana iri mw’ijuru ubwami bwiwe ni buniniya yuko itazoba zanira igihuhusi kivanzwe mwo umusenyi n’amabuye, niho muzomenya ituza ryanje"
  67,18,"Ntankeka barahakanye abariho imbere yabo, mbega kwabaye gute ugushavura kwanje"
  67,19,"Mbega ntibabona inyoni ziri hejuru yabo ingene zigorora amababa yazo n’ukuyazinga, nta n’umwe azi zitirira atari Imana nyene imigisha myinshi, mu vy’ukuri niyo ibona ibintu vyose"
  67,20,Canke n’izihe ngabo zanyu zishobora kuba kingira atari nyene imigisha myinshi? Ntaba hakanyi b’Imana yabo y’ukuri atari uguhendwa gusa
  67,21,Canke ni nde azobaha imigisha mugihe ibazitiriye iyo migisha yayo ahubwo babandanya mu bwiyonkore bwabo n’urwankano gusa
  67,22,"Mbega uwugenda ajunjamitse umutwe wiwe atamerewe neza, mbega niwe mweranda, canke uwugenda atumbereye inzira igororotse"
  67,23,"Vuga uti:- niyo yabaremye n’ukubaha amatwi n’amaso hamwe n’imitima, rero nibakeyi cane bashima iyo ngabirano yanyu"
  67,24,"Vuga uti:- niyo yabatandukanije kw’Isi, niwe niho muzo kwegeranywa"
  67,25,"Nabo bavuga bati:- niryari iryo sango nimwaba mu vugisha ukuri"
  67,26,"Vuga uti :- ubumenyi bwavyo buri ku Mana, kandi mu vy’ukuri jewe ndi umutuza gusa n’uwuba sobanurira"
  67,27,"Mugabo mugihe bazo kibonera kiri hafi, amaso y’abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri azo mara mara hanyuma havurwe hati:- ibi nivyo mwahora musaba"
  67,28,"Vuga uti:- ni mumbwire yuko Imana niya mponya jewe, hamwe nabo turi kumwe, canke itugiriye impuhwe zayo, none ni nde azoba kingira abo bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri n’ibihano vy’Imana bibabaza"
  67,29,"Vuga uti:- Imana niyo nyene impuhwe nyinshi twebwe tuyemera n’ukuyizera, nubu vuba muzo menya uwuri m’ubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  67,30,"Vuga uti:- mwebwe mubona gute nkiyo amazi yanyu yoba yibijwe mu kuzimu, none ni nde yobazanira amazi meza y’isoko"